00:44:01,180 --> 00:44:04,500
What is she singing for?

785
00:44:04,700 --> 00:44:07,980
The wind caresses the hills

786
00:44:08,140 --> 00:44:11,420
The wind causes ripples on calm water

787
00:44:11,550 --> 00:44:17,220
Moonlight graces passing souls

788
00:44:46,180 --> 00:44:49,340
Her steps get slower and slower

789
00:44:49,460 --> 00:44:52,740
She's trod a lengthy path

790
00:44:52,980 --> 00:44:56,220
Memories lost then found

791
00:44:56,500 --> 00:44:59,620
Gazing idly as clouds roll by

792
00:44:59,940 --> 00:45:03,020
She holds a red candle

793
00:45:03,380 --> 00:45:06,660
To brave the thick fog

794
00:45:06,820 --> 00:45:10,100
Life can be bitter sometimes

795
00:45:10,380 --> 00:45:13,620
Experience it with grace

796
00:45:13,780 --> 00:45:17,060
Like a fleeting dream

